

CapeGamini
============

Strong proficiency in React 
Experience with Server-Side Rendering and/or NodeJS a plus. 
Knowledge of React Router is ideal and other frameworks like Remix / NextJS a plus. 
Knowledge of Tailwind a plus. 
Strong understanding of TypeScript. 
Solid knowledge of C# and .NET/ASP.NET Core 
REST APIs and microservice architecture
Familiarity with asynchronous communication (message queues, event buses)
Azure knowledge such as integration with Cosmos DB a plus
General Developer Proficiency 
Experience with testing (unit, integration, end-to-end)
Knowledge of CI/CD 
Proficiency in Git version control 
Understanding of agile methodologies 

The following experience is advantageous: 

Proven experience in .Net development and Oracle databases 
Extensive knowledge of SQL PL/SQL and experience with cloud database technologies. Added bonus would be SSRS & SSIS 
Experience with cloud platforms such as Azure or AWS and building cloud native applications 
Familiarity with microservices and container-based architecture (e.g. Docker Kubernetes) 
Knowledge of API design and development. Web API and Web Services 
Front-end React Native 
Strong problem-solving skills with the ability to translate complex problems into simpler parts 
Excellent communication skills both written and verbal. Ability to be client facing 
A team player with the ability to work effectively with others to achieve common goals 
Ability to stay informed about the latest advancements in tech and translating them into feasible plans 